<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>WanderMap</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: url('/images/background.jpg') no-repeat center center fixed;
      background-size: cover;
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: left;
      height: 100vh;
      text-align: left;
      padding-left: 55px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 4rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      text-shadow: 1px 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    }

    button {
      padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
      color: #333;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    button:hover {
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>WanderMap</h1>
  <p>Track your travels, journal your memories, and capture your adventures on your very own travel map.</p>
  <a href="/index"><button>Happy Wandering</button></a>
</body>
</html>
